OL,3,CCriminals to face being banned from
OL,4,Cpubs under new sentencing powers
OL,6,FCriminals could be banned from pubs,
OL,7,Fconcerts and sports grounds under
OL,8,Fplans to give judges powers to pass
OL,9,Ftougher community sentences.
OL,11,FOffenders could face limits on
OL,12,Fdriving, travel bans and restriction
OL,13,Fzones confining them to specific areas
OL,14,Funder the proposals, which would apply
OL,15,Fin England and Wales.
OL,17,FThose who break the conditions could
OL,18,Fface being dragged back in front of a
OL,19,Fjudge and given a tougher punishment.
