OL,3,CCriminals to face being banned from
OL,4,Cpubs under new sentencing powers
OL,6,FSimilar restrictions could also apply
OL,7,Fto prisoners let out on licence, while
OL,8,Fmandatory drug testing will also be
OL,9,Fexpanded to cover all those released.
OL,11,FThe crisis in prison places has led
OL,12,Fthe Government to explore alternatives
OL,13,Fto custody.
OL,15,FCourts already have the power to
OL,16,Fimpose conditions on certain
OL,17,Fsentences, such as banning football
OL,18,Fhooligans from grounds, but the new
OL,19,Fmeasures would allow them to be
OL,20,Fimposed for any offence.
