OL,3,CCriminals to face being banned from
OL,4,Cpubs under new sentencing powers
OL,6,FJustice Secretary Shabana Mahmood
OL,7,Fsaid: "When criminals break society's
OL,8,Frules, they must be punished.
OL,10,F"Those serving their sentences in the
OL,11,Fcommunity must have their freedom
OL,12,Frestricted there too.
OL,14,F"These new punishments should remind
OL,15,Fall offenders that, under this
OL,16,FGovernment, crime does not pay.
OL,18,F"Rightly, the public expect the
OL,19,FGovernment to do everything in its
OL,20,Fpower to keep Britain safe, and that's
OL,21,Fwhat we're doing."
