OL,3,CCriminals to face being banned from
OL,4,Cpubs under new sentencing powers
OL,6,FThe Government will bring forward
OL,7,Flegislation for the new powers, which
OL,8,Fwill be monitored by probation
OL,9,Fofficers.
OL,11,FCourts will be able to hand out the
OL,12,Fconditions to criminals given
OL,13,Fcommunity or suspended sentences,
OL,14,Fwhile probation officers will be able
OL,15,Fto set them as part of the terms for
OL,16,Foffenders on licence.
